" style=\"background:#6a8360\">Get started</a>\n                <a href=\"#\" class=\"primary-button is-p-r\"><svg class=\"arrow-icon\" viewBox=\"0 0 8 5\" fill=\"none\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4.32517 0.0354578L5.42397 1.6028e-07L8 2.51064L5.4458 5L4.3052 4.96635L5.57012 3.73355C5.878 3.43348 6.15998 3.16461 6.41658 2.92694L0.205982 2.9077L0.244359 2.0731L6.45486 2.09244C6.20397 1.86046 5.92658 1.59621 5.62262 1.29997L4.32517 0.0354578Z\" fill=\"currentColor\"/><path d=\"M0.82393 2.00287e-07L0.82393 2.90815H0L2.64111e-07 1.65186e-07L0.82393 2.00287e-07Z\" fill=\"currentColor\"/></svg>Learn more</a>\n              </div>\n            </article>\n            <a href=\"#\" class=\"safety-link\">Important Safety Information</a>\n          </li>\n\n          <li class=\"product-slide\" role=\"listitem\">\n            <article class=\"product-card\">\n              <div class=\"card-top\">\n                <div class=\"product-title-div\"><div class=\"heading-6\">Mounjaro®</div><div class=\"rx-text\">Rx</div></div>\n                <div class=\"subheading-card\" style=\"color:#6a8360\">FDA approved for weight loss</div>\n              </div>\n              <div class=\"video-card-visual\">\n                <img class=\"video-card-visual__img\" src=\"assets/mounjaro.avif\" alt=\"Mounjaro injection pen\" loading=\"lazy\">\n              </div>\n              <div class=\"card-buttons-flex\">\n                <a href=\"#\" class=\"primary-button is-p-l\" style=\"background:#6a8360\">Get started</a>\n                <a href=\"#\" class=\"primary-button is-p-r\"><svg class=\"arrow-icon\" viewBox=\"0 0 8 5\" fill=\"none\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4.32517 0.0354578L5.42397 1.6028e-07L8 2.51064L5.4458 5L4.3052 4.96635L5.57012 3.73355C5.878 3.43348 6.15998 3.16461 6.41658 2.92694L0.205982 2.9077L0.244359 2.0731L6.45486 2.09244C6.20397 1.86046 5.92658 1.59621 5.62262 1.29997L4.32517 0.0354578Z\" fill=\"currentColor\"/><path d=\"M0.82393 2.00287e-07L0.82393 2.90815H0L2.64111e-07 1.65186e-07L0.82393 2.00287e-07Z\" fill=\"currentColor\"/></svg>Learn more</a>\n              </div>\n            </article>\n            <a href=\"#\" class=\"safety-link\">Important Safety Information</a>\n          </li>\n\n        </ul>\n      </div>\n\n      <div class=\"gsap-slider__controls\">\n        <button type=\"button\" class=\"gsap-slider__control\" data-nav=\"prev\" aria-label=\"Previous\">\n          <svg class=\"slider-arrow is-left\" viewBox=\"0 0 12 8\" fill=\"none\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M6.34208 0.0567323L8.03384 0L12 4.01702L8.06744 8L6.31133 7.94616L8.25885 5.97367C8.73288 5.49356 9.16703 5.06338 9.56209 4.68311L0 4.65232L0.0590857 3.31696L9.62103 3.3479C9.23475 2.97674 8.80767 2.55394 8.33968 2.07995L6.34208 0.0567323Z\" fill=\"currentColor\"/></svg>\n        </button>\n        <button type=\"button\" class=\"gsap-slider__control\" data-nav=\"next\" aria-label=\"Next\">\n          <svg class=\"slider-arrow\" viewBox=\"0 0 12 8\" fill=\"none\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M6.34208 0.0567323L8.03384 0L12 4.01702L8.06744 8L6.31133 7.94616L8.25885 5.97367C8.73288 5.49356 9.16703 5.06338 9.56209 4.68311L0 4.65232L0.0590857 3.31696L9.62103 3.3479C9.23475 2.97674 8.80767 2.55394 8.33968 2.07995L6.34208 0.0567323Z\" fill=\"currentColor\"/></svg>\n        </button>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n\n  <div class=\"products-subsection\">\n    <div class=\"products-subsection-grid\">\n      <div>\n        <h3 class=\"h-max-width\">Achieve your <span class=\"is-wl-text\">weight loss</span> goals</h3>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"featured-content\">\n        <p class=\"p-max-width\">Explore our weight loss medications to learn how they work, or complete a quick medical intake to get personalized guidance from a licensed provider.</p>\n        <div class=\"cta-flex\">\n          <a href=\"#\" class=\"primary-button is-secondary\">\n            <svg class=\"arrow-icon\" viewBox=\"0 0 8 5\" fill=\"none\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4.32517 0.0354578L5.42397 1.6028e-07L8 2.51064L5.4458 5L4.3052 4.96635L5.57012 3.73355C5.878 3.43348 6.15998 3.16461 6.41658 2.92694L0.205982 2.9077L0.244359 2.0731L6.45486 2.09244C6.20397 1.86046 5.92658 1.59621 5.62262 1.29997L4.32517 0.0354578Z\" fill=\"currentColor\"/><path d=\"M0.82393 2.00287e-07L0.82393 2.90815H0L2.64111e-07 1.65186e-07L0.82393 2.00287e-07Z\" fill=\"currentColor\"/></svg>\n            Explore Weight Loss\n          </a>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</section>\n\n<script>\n/* Carousel: drag-to-scroll + arrow navigation, mirrors what the original\n   gsap Draggable + scroll-snap setup does without the GSAP dependency.\n   - Pointer drag: convert pointer-x delta to scrollLeft, suspend scroll-snap\n     while dragging so the user-controlled scroll feels continuous.\n   - Arrow buttons: shift one card width per click. We disable each button\n     when the relevant edge is reached. */\n(function () {\n  const track = document.querySelector('[data-track]');\n  if (!track) return;\n  const prevBtn = document.querySelector('[data-nav=\"prev\"]');\n  const nextBtn = document.querySelector('[data-nav=\"next\"]');\n\n  const cardStep = () => {\n    const card = track.querySelector('.product-slide');\n    if (!card) return 400;\n    const styles = getComputedStyle(track.querySelector('.gsap-slider__list'));\n    const gap = parseFloat(styles.columnGap || styles.gap) || 0;\n    return card.getBoundingClientRect().width + gap;\n  };\n\n  const updateBtns = () => {\n    const max = track.scrollWidth - track.clientWidth;\n    prevBtn.setAttribute('aria-disabled', track.scrollLeft <= 1 ? 'true' : 'false');\n    nextBtn.setAttribute('aria-disabled', track.scrollLeft >= max - 1 ? 'true' : 'false');\n  };\n\n  prevBtn.addEventListener('click', () => track.scrollBy({ left: -cardStep(), behavior: 'smooth' }));\n  nextBtn.addEventListener('click', () => track.scrollBy({ left:  cardStep(), behavior: 'smooth' }));\n  track.addEventListener('scroll', updateBtns, { passive: true });\n  window.addEventListener('resize', updateBtns);\n  updateBtns();\n\n  /* hover-spin video: any product-card containing a <video> swaps the still\n     for the looping mp4 on mouseenter. Original Webflow site uses a Bunny\n     Stream player + data-video-on-hover controller for the same swap. */\n  document.querySelectorAll('.product-card').forEach(card => {\n    const video = card.querySelector('.video-card-visual__video');\n    if (!video || !video.getAttribute('src')) return;\n    card.addEventListener('mouseenter', () => {\n      card.classList.add('is-playing');\n      video.play().catch(() => {});\n    });\n    card.addEventListener('mouseleave', () => {\n      card.classList.remove('is-playing');\n      try { video.pause(); video.currentTime = 0; } catch {}\n    });\n  });\n\n  // pointer drag — desktop \"grab and pull\" UX (mobile uses native touch scroll)\n  let isDown = false, startX = 0, startScroll = 0, moved = 0;\n  track.addEventListener('pointerdown', (e) => {\n    if (e.pointerType !== 'mouse') return; // touch handled natively\n    isDown = true; moved = 0;\n    startX = e.clientX;\n    startScroll = track.scrollLeft;\n    track.classList.add('is-dragging');\n    track.setPointerCapture(e.pointerId);\n  });\n  track.addEventListener('pointermove', (e) => {\n    if (!isDown) return;\n    const dx = e.clientX - startX;\n    moved = Math.max(moved, Math.abs(dx));\n    track.scrollLeft = startScroll - dx;\n  });\n  const release = (e) => {\n    if (!isDown) return;\n    isDown = false;\n    track.classList.remove('is-dragging');\n    try { track.releasePointerCapture(e.pointerId); } catch {}\n  };\n  track.addEventListener('pointerup', release);\n  track.addEventListener('pointercancel', release);\n  // suppress click-through after a real drag (>5px)\n  track.addEventListener('click', (e) => { if (moved > 5) { e.preventDefault(); e.stopPropagation(); } }, true);\n})();\n</script>\n\n<!-- sc2-overlay:start -->\n<style>\n  #sc2-overlay {\n    position: fixed; top: 16px; right: 16px; z-index: 2147483647;\n    display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 8px;\n    font: 600 12px/1 -apple-system, \"Segoe UI\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", Helvetica, sans-serif;\n  }\n  #sc2-overlay .sc2-btn {\n    display: inline-flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;\n    padding: 8px 14px; min-width: 110px;\n    color: #fff; background: rgba(20,22,30,.78);\n    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.16); border-radius: 8px;\n    text-decoration: none;\n    -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(10px); backdrop-filter: blur(10px);\n    box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(0,0,0,.2);\n    transition: background .15s, transform .15s;\n  }\n  #sc2-overlay .sc2-btn:hover {\n    background: rgba(20,22,30,.95); transform: translateY(-1px);\n  }\n</style>\n<div id=\"sc2-overlay\">\n  <a class=\"sc2-btn\" href=\"010-glm-weight-loss-carousel.zip\" download title=\"下载本 effect 的 zip 包\">📦 下载 zip</a>\n  <a class=\"sc2-btn\" href=\"../view.html?effect=010-glm-weight-loss-carousel\" target=\"_top\" title=\"查看 / 复制源码\">📋 源码</a>\n</div>\n<script>\n(function () {\n  if (new URLSearchParams(location.search).get('demo') === 'preview') {\n    var el = document.getElementById('sc2-overlay');\n    if (el) el.remove();\n  }\n})();\n</script>\n<!-- sc2-overlay:end -->\n</body>\n</html>\n"
